{"tid":2034094,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"串謀獲試題案　蕭源被判監14個月","createTime":"2020-05-25T04:46:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-25T05:14:31.000Z","uid":187876,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"0aee325a71f630f81882f6546ad2bad4979e10f3","tid":2034094,"uid":187876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T04:46:06.000Z","msg":"著名中文科補習導師蕭源，被指串謀2名擔任中學文憑試中國語文科口試主考員的大學同學，分別使他們向蕭洩露試題和評分準則，以供蕭在Facebook發布試題和應考策略，3人早前被裁定兩項串謀公職人員行為失當罪罪成，蕭源今(25日)在屯門法院被判監14個月，另外二人則分別被判監8個月，以及監禁5個月緩刑兩年。<br />\n3名被告包括蕭志勇（即蕭源，42歲）、張國權（43歲）、吳宏樑（43歲）。蕭在案發時是現代教育的中國語文科導師，張、吳分別在佛教沈香林紀念中學和香港華仁書院任教中文科。<br />\n蕭和張被控於2016年3月10日至22日，串謀使張蓄意向蕭披露口試試題。蕭與吳則被控於2017年3月1日至9日，串謀使吳蓄意向蕭披露該科的評分準則。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200525/bkn-20200525123956288-0525_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20200525%2Fbkn-20200525123956288-0525_00822_001.html&d=g30fgRh1OaLpBbOto8aU3l3VpWtqcNNCzs9YdIyDBYU%3D&h=f6671c01\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200525/bkn-20200525123956288-0525_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"23e5bf3a6c093e618c8f86d250eba768f925cb28","tid":2034094,"uid":147916,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T04:46:37.000Z","msg":"咁少，益佢啦屌"},{"pid":"45a1dd3faa90e8d8d29a1066d9f049e9c0052a0d","tid":2034094,"uid":42374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T04:47:03.000Z","msg":"牙kris點解唔使坐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b28afd319db07a90db0bbf12f0ed4992bca0bbb","tid":2034094,"uid":71195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T04:47:32.000Z","msg":"檸檬茶<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45002650440002b4f166837776034fd398ce49f9","tid":2034094,"uid":222970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T04:48:25.000Z","msg"